OL,3,CWhat are potholes costing motorists ?
OL,4,CNew data exposes depth of problem
OL,6,FJanuary 15 is National Pothole Day,
OL,7,Festablished by an alliance of road
OL,8,Fexperts.
OL,10,FBut for drivers in many parts of the
OL,11,FUK - every day is pothole day.
OL,13,FIf only promises could fill potholes
OL,14,Fbecause over the years officials have
OL,15,Fpledged long term fixes that never
OL,16,Fseem to arrive.
OL,18,FNew figures from the RAC on Wednesday
OL,19,Fshow the average cost of pothole
OL,20,Fdamage to a vehicle is now #460.
