OL,3,CWhat are potholes costing motorists ?
OL,4,CNew data exposes depth of problem
OL,6,FI spoke to Alan Piggott who owns
OL,7,Fgarage in Cambridgeshire which repairs
OL,8,Falmost 2,000 alloy wheels a year due
OL,9,Fto pothole damage.
OL,11,F"Over the last three years we've seen
OL,12,Fpothole damage increase three-fold,
OL,13,Fwheels and tyres are fundamental for
OL,14,Fsafety," he told ITV News.
OL,16,FFor taxpayers potholes have become a
OL,17,Fmoney pit with #1.6 billion for
OL,18,FEngland alone form central government
OL,19,Fthis financial year.
OL,21,FBut is it being spent wisely?
